name: Tezzy Everydays #8 | Queen Hen | May 8th, 2021
description: This is the eighth day of my 1 of 1 pixel art series. Every pixel art piece will involve everyones favorite coin, which most certainly is Tezos. I decided to go with a strong female character in my punk style today. Queen Hen is an NFT and crypto expert teaching people about self empowerment through art and peer to peer transactions. Tezzy Everydays are created by @clipdad_
